701899f-a.title: Bronx: Tilden Street - Barnes Avenue
701899f-a.text:
Tilden Street (6-story building thereon), between Barnes Ave. and
East Gunhill Road. The 6-story house is on the north side of the street
and is called the Tilden Apartments. The view is northeastward from
East Gunhill Road.
June 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
